OL,3,CRefugee charity seeks new Bristol home
OL,4,Cas demand reaches record levels
OL,6,FA charity supporting refugees and
OL,7,Fasylum seekers in Bristol is in such
OL,8,Fhigh demand it's urgently searching
OL,9,Ffor bigger premises.
OL,11,FAid Box Community has received around
OL,12,F6,500 enquiries in the last year, up
OL,13,Ffrom nearly 5,000 the year before.
OL,15,FThe record levels of need means the
OL,16,Fcharity, which started in 2015 to help
OL,17,Fmigrants in northern France, has
OL,18,Foutgrown its current home. the lease
OL,19,Fon which expires in July.
