OL,3,CRefugee charity seeks new Bristol home
OL,4,Cas demand reaches record levels
OL,6,FMore than a thousand people who've
OL,7,Ffled conflicts and persecution in
OL,8,Ftheir own country have been placed in
OL,9,Fthe city by the Home Office, many
OL,10,Fwaiting years before their futures are
OL,11,Fdecided.
OL,13,FWith no right to work, the asylum
OL,14,Fseekers are reliant on hand-outs which
OL,15,Fare provided at ABC's free shop on
OL,16,FCheltenham Road.
