OL,3,CRefugee charity seeks new Bristol home
OL,4,Cas demand reaches record levels
OL,6,FMohamed Abdalla had a marketing job in
OL,7,FQatar before his company shutdown just
OL,8,Fas his homeland of Sudan plunged into
OL,9,Fcivil war. The 41-year-old and his
OL,10,Ffamily couldn't gain entry to nearby
OL,11,Fcountries so fled to the UK.JHe said:
OL,12,F"Everything has gone."
