OL,3,CRefugee charity seeks new Bristol home
OL,4,Cas demand reaches record levels
OL,6,FFor the last eight months, with his
OL,7,Fwife and three young children, Mohamed
OL,8,Fhas been a living in a Bristol city
OL,9,Fcentre hotel.JMohamed said: "We are
OL,10,Ftrying to cope with the situation. We
OL,11,Fare living in two rooms but it's a
OL,12,Fmatter of how you keep yourself
OL,13,Ftogether and try to survive. I
OL,14,Funderstand it is not heaven but you
OL,15,Fhave to work with what you have."JHe
OL,16,Fgives back by volunteering at ABC
OL,17,Fwhile waiting for permission to
OL,18,Fremain. He's confident it will arrive,
OL,19,Fless sure of when.
