OL,3,CRefugee charity seeks new Bristol home
OL,4,Cas demand reaches record levels
OL,6,FImogen said: "As our service has
OL,7,Fevolved, we now need more physical
OL,8,Fspace so people can connect and help
OL,9,Four team work in a more suitable
OL,10,Fenvironment. We need a place of
OL,11,Fbetween 3,000 and 5,000 sq ft, and can
OL,12,Fpay rent for the next three years at
OL,13,Fleast."
OL,15,FThe charity has a budget of #45,000 a
OL,16,Fyear to spend on new premises,
OL,17,Fpreferably outside the Clean Air Zone
OL,18,F(CAZ), while still being as central as
OL,19,Fpossible and near a bus route,
OL,20,Fpreferably north of the city centre.
