OL,3,CRefugee charity seeks new Bristol home
OL,4,Cas demand reaches record levels
OL,6,FMother-of-three Mehbooba Ferdoush won
OL,7,Fher right to remain after a three-year
OL,8,Fwait for a Home Office decision. A
OL,9,Fpolitical activist in Bangladesh, she
OL,10,Fwas an opponent of the ruling regime
OL,11,Fand hasn't returned to her homeland
OL,12,Fand family in more than a decade.JShe
OL,13,Fsaid: "It was a very very hard time
OL,14,Fbut if you are in need, Aid Box
OL,15,FCommunity are there. I always get
OL,16,Femotional when I talk about them
OL,17,Fbecause it is a huge support. I feel
OL,18,FAid Box Community is my second home."
